Params: {3: 'The space crumbles in an instant as twisted time and space blend into disordered rhythms, alternating through chaotic tracks to create a symphony without structure.'}
{3: 'Nebulae spin into disrupted shapes as your dimensional perception gradually blurs. You can no longer discern how long the battle here has lasted—is it one second? Or ten thousand years?'}
{3: 'You stand alone, facing the vast cosmic domain yet showing no trace of fear.'}
{3: 'Failing again and again, yet rising each time, all M.I.N.D.s once connected with your Mind Beacon converge into a faint light—'}
{3: 'The frail spark has already set the world ablaze.'}
{3: "Countless pasts and futures overlap as bonds and causality envelop you. Innumerable failures pile corpses into towering monuments, only to crumble into sand under time's destructive force."}
{3: 'Battles from the past come sweeping back with earth-shattering force, horrific wounds accumulating one after another in both flesh and spirit.'}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> The rust-eaten gear started to turn slowly.'}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> The dark star fell from the sky, casting a shadow across the earth.'}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> The crimson hue reaped the moving paradise.'}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> The nocturnal voyage stretched on endlessly, guiding Kowloong back to the grand city.'}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> Blood became eroded, dawn submerged beneath the tide.'}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> The night of calamity arrived in a fabricated tomorrow.'}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> Hope was seen emerge from the depths of the sea.'}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> Amidst the nightmarish battle, new life arrived.'}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> The girl declared war on the Eternal Night.'}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> The shadow of the past returned in the dead of night.'}
{3: 'Fight, in this battle endless and infinite.'}
{3: 'In the eternal stillness of the long night, you raise your gun against the higher-dimensional being amid the sea of stars.'}
{3: 'Gunpowder smoke fills the air as deeper fears, accompanied by mournful cries, are crushed and scattered around you.'}
{3: "COMMANDANT<//WE> The crimson light pierced through the sky's dome."}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> The corrupted forest whispered of an unknown lifeform.'}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> The ocean lifted a morning star.'}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> The memorial fire kindled deep sorrow.'}
{3: "COMMANDANT<//WE> Daylight lingered in the world's forgotten depths."}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> Moonlight was imprisoned within the red nightmare.'}
{3: 'COMMANDANT<//WE> Tears soaked through the crimson abyss.'}
{1: '"Even so... Do you still wish to continue?"', 3: '60'}
{3: '"Even so... Do you still wish to continue?"'}
{2: '—I will never surrender the chance to fight.', 3: '166', 4: "—I will never abandon humanity's future.", 5: '166', 6: '—I will never leave Lucia behind.', 7: '160'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'I can overcome anything with you and Gray Raven by my side, just like always.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Faith and courage flow ceaselessly from your Mind Beacon.'}
{3: 'Faith and courage flow ceaselessly from your Mind Beacon.'}
{3: 'In the timeless quiet, you rise anew, infinite hues ablaze in the depths of your gaze.'}
{3: 'On the distant horizon, stars emerge and perish within a dazzling explosion, stardust fragments raining down in glittering splendor.'}
{3: 'At the boundary between life and death, you stare directly at the being whose form defies description.'}
{3: 'The voice of the universe echoes hollow and pale.'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Lee takes aim at the unknown being, his finger pressing the trigger with a resolute click.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Lucia shadows close behind, springing up in a single leap as her blade slices toward the silhouette.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 3: "Liv's fingers clench around her scepter as a domain of power unfurls—", 4: '3'}
{3: 'It all ends with a gunshot from your hands.'}
{3: 'The higher-dimensional being wipes away her "wound" and sheds her disguise.'}
{3: 'A lingering sigh resonates through the void as this prolonged "battle" at last concludes beneath the united onslaught of four people.'}
{3: 'The Observer slowly ceases her movements as her "projection" begins to dissipate.'}
{3: 'Endless exhaustion floods your brain. Your consciousness is plunged into searing seawater in an instant—so scalding that not even a whisper can escape your vocal cords.'}
{3: 'Your eyes slowly close within the suffocating darkness as large patches of vibrant colors flash across your retinas.'}
{3: 'Rage, helplessness, joy, fear, agony—countless emotions erupt simultaneously in your mind as infinite specks of light gradually reconstruct everything here...'}
{1: '"The moment they reach the unopened door in their bodies of flesh and blood—"', 3: '60'}
{3: '"The moment they reach the unopened door in their bodies of flesh and blood—"'}
